01:20:29.283 --> 01:20:32.980
I don't feel bad for you. I know you
got a thing going on with Candace.

01:20:36.791 --> 01:20:38.258
Candace and Bernice?

01:20:40.795 --> 01:20:42.660
Candace, Bernice and Rose?

01:20:44.799 --> 01:20:48.428
Yeah. I fell for one chick and I'm losing
my mind. Good luck with that.

01:20:48.803 --> 01:20:50.202
Okay, baby.

01:20:50.304 --> 01:20:51.965
I love you.

01:20:52.306 --> 01:20:54.774
Thanks, buddy.
Remember to use a condom.

01:20:55.309 --> 01:20:57.300
Or in your case, a Hefty bag.

01:21:07.822 --> 01:21:09.255
Well...

01:21:09.323 --> 01:21:12.417
Okay, you guys. Thanks for coming
to say goodbye.

01:21:12.827 --> 01:21:14.522
Be careful.

01:21:14.829 --> 01:21:17.764
You make sure your father doesn't
get eaten by a shark.

01:21:24.338 --> 01:21:27.273
Thank you, buddy.
What does that mean again?

01:21:27.842 --> 01:21:29.639
Bring me back a T-shirt.

01:21:29.844 --> 01:21:32.176
Oh, okay. You got it.

01:21:32.847 --> 01:21:35.042
Come here. All right. Love you guys.

01:21:35.850 --> 01:21:38.785
My shirt size is medium husky.

01:21:40.855 --> 01:21:43.153
Hey! Kikikuloa!

01:21:43.357 --> 01:21:46.155
No flippies off the dock!
You could get hurt!

01:21:48.863 --> 01:21:53.732
No! All right. Let the master
show you how to get it done.

01:22:01.876 --> 01:22:05.505
Now you kids go down there
and find my nuts.

01:22:05.880 --> 01:22:07.711
Sure you don't want to take Doug?

01:22:07.882 --> 01:22:11.511
Hey! What the heck
are you guys doing here?

01:22:11.886 --> 01:22:16.448
I spoke to the harbormaster and he
said you were setting sail today...

01:22:16.483 --> 01:22:18.620
...so we thought we'd wish
you bon voyage.

01:22:18.893 --> 01:22:21.885
This is from Nick and Sue.
They send their best wishes.

01:22:22.396 --> 01:22:26.230
That's very nice.
Spam and Reese's. All right.

01:22:26.400 --> 01:22:28.800
I love Spam and Reese's.
Can I have it?

01:22:28.903 --> 01:22:30.495
I guess.

01:22:31.405 --> 01:22:33.498
- Doug!
- That's all right.

01:22:33.533 --> 01:22:36.433
- I'm sorry.
- So...

01:22:37.411 --> 01:22:38.673
...how's Lucy?

01:22:39.413 --> 01:22:42.143
Actually, she's living at the institute.

01:22:42.917 --> 01:22:46.284
- When did that happen?
- Three weeks ago.

01:22:46.921 --> 01:22:50.652
Said she didn't want to be a burden to
me and Doug anymore. I don't know.

01:22:50.925 --> 01:22:53.393
I couldn't talk her out of it.
You know what?

01:22:53.427 --> 01:22:55.622
She's doing really great up there.

01:22:55.930 --> 01:22:58.990
She's teaching an art class
and she gets to paint every day.

01:22:59.433 --> 01:23:01.264
In fact, she's even singing again.

01:23:01.435 --> 01:23:03.630
Hey, look, I got a little gift
for you too.

01:23:03.938 --> 01:23:07.738
It's just a little something
from one sailor to another one.

01:23:09.443 --> 01:23:11.377
You take care of yourself out there.

01:23:11.946 --> 01:23:14.380
- I will.
- Okay.

01:23:22.957 --> 01:23:24.891
Henry did not tell me about you.

01:23:24.959 --> 01:23:27.553
Your fisherman muscles.

01:23:28.462 --> 01:23:29.724
Can I touch?

01:23:29.964 --> 01:23:31.795
Sure.

01:23:37.471 --> 01:23:39.405
Yes.

01:23:46.981 --> 01:23:48.278
The Beach Boys?

01:23:48.482 --> 01:23:51.349
How nice of him to give me a CD
that will remind me...

01:23:51.986 --> 01:23:55.444
...of all the wonderful times
I shared with his daughter.

01:23:55.489 --> 01:23:57.889
What an asshole!

01:24:16.510 --> 01:24:18.535
Oh, why?

01:24:19.013 --> 01:24:21.345
Why would you do this to me?

01:24:21.515 --> 01:24:24.040
You sick bastard!

01:24:28.522 --> 01:24:30.080
Oh, my God.

01:24:31.025 --> 01:24:32.959
Is he trying to tell me something?

01:24:37.531 --> 01:24:39.965
She only sings on days
she meets you.

01:24:42.036 --> 01:24:44.004
She remembers me?

01:24:44.538 --> 01:24:46.130
Holy shit!

01:24:47.541 --> 01:24:50.305
She remembers me!

01:24:55.549 --> 01:24:57.466
Julia, that looks great.

01:24:57.501 --> 01:24:59.383
Excuse me. What am I doing?

01:25:00.054 --> 01:25:03.319
You're painting a picture.
And you're doing an excellent job.

01:25:03.557 --> 01:25:05.184
Oh.

01:25:06.560 --> 01:25:09.586
Holy crap! I suck.

01:25:18.072 --> 01:25:19.767
Hey, hey, hey.

01:25:20.074 --> 01:25:22.907
- Can we help you, sir?
- Yes. I have an appointment.

01:25:23.077 --> 01:25:25.511
- What's your name?
- My name?

01:25:28.082 --> 01:25:31.279
Dude, he forgot his name.
I feel bad for him.

01:25:31.585 --> 01:25:34.486
Just go on up. And good luck
with that memory problem.

01:25:34.588 --> 01:25:36.579
Yeah. Thank you.

01:25:38.592 --> 01:25:39.889
What?

01:25:40.594 --> 01:25:42.687
Lucy!

01:25:43.097 --> 01:25:44.792
Lucy!

01:25:45.099 --> 01:25:47.749
- Hi, I'm Tom.
- Hey, I met you before. I'm Henry.

01:25:47.784 --> 01:25:50.399
Maybe you can help me.
I'm looking for Lucy Whitmore.

01:25:50.604 --> 01:25:52.128
Any idea where I can find her?

01:25:52.606 --> 01:25:53.572
Hi, I'm Tom.

01:25:53.607 --> 01:25:56.576
Oh. Thanks anyways.

01:25:57.611 --> 01:25:59.476
Lucy!

01:26:00.114 --> 01:26:01.581
Lucy!

01:26:05.619 --> 01:26:07.382
Lucy Whitmore...

01:26:08.622 --> 01:26:10.487
...can I ask you a question?

01:26:13.627 --> 01:26:15.822
Do you have any idea who I am?

01:26:22.136 --> 01:26:25.299
- No.
- No?

01:26:26.640 --> 01:26:28.665
That sucks.

01:26:30.144 --> 01:26:33.136
- What's your name?
- I'm Henry.

01:26:33.647 --> 01:26:35.410
Henry.

01:26:36.650 --> 01:26:39.517
I want to show you something.
Will you come with me?

01:26:40.154 --> 01:26:41.553
Well, yeah.

01:26:43.157 --> 01:26:45.091
Hey. Do you know who that guy is?

01:26:45.159 --> 01:26:47.320
Dude, I don't even know who I am.

01:26:47.661 --> 01:26:49.925
Oh, well, you're Pablo Picasso.

01:26:50.164 --> 01:26:53.861
- Really?
- No. Not really.

01:26:57.171 --> 01:26:59.833
This is my studio.

01:27:19.193 --> 01:27:21.855
I don't know who you are, Henry...

01:27:23.697 --> 01:27:27.633
...but I dream about you
almost every night.

01:27:30.204 --> 01:27:31.728
Why?

01:27:32.206 --> 01:27:36.267
What would you say if I told you
that notebook you read every day...

01:27:36.710 --> 01:27:39.736
...used to have a lot of stuff
about me in it?

01:27:41.215 --> 01:27:43.809
I would say that that
makes a lot of sense.

01:27:44.218 --> 01:27:46.015
You erased me
from your memories...

01:27:46.220 --> 01:27:49.383
...because you thought you were
holding me back from having...

01:27:49.723 --> 01:27:51.452
...a full and happy life.

01:27:51.725 --> 01:27:54.216
But you made a mistake.

01:27:54.728 --> 01:27:58.357
Being with you is the only way
I could have a full and happy life.

01:27:59.233 --> 01:28:01.497
You're the girl of my dreams...

01:28:01.735 --> 01:28:05.501
...and apparently I'm the man of yours.

01:28:10.244 --> 01:28:12.007
Henry.

01:28:12.246 --> 01:28:13.645
It's nice to meet you.

01:28:14.248 --> 01:28:17.240
Lucy, it's nice to meet you too.

01:28:21.755 --> 01:28:23.723
Hi, I'm Tom.

01:28:23.757 --> 01:28:25.918
Henry, Lucy. Nice to meet you, Tom.

01:28:26.260 --> 01:28:29.889
Now why don't you come back in
ten seconds so we can meet again?

01:29:15.309 --> 01:29:18.904
Do you, Honah Lee, take this woman
to be your lawfully wedded wife...

01:29:18.939 --> 01:29:21.178
...to have and to hold
from this day forth...

01:29:21.815 --> 01:29:23.908
...as long as you both shall live?

01:29:23.943 --> 01:29:25.785
- I do.
- Really?

01:29:26.320 --> 01:29:28.515
Even though in, like, 10, 15 years...

01:29:28.822 --> 01:29:31.518
...she could possibly let herself
go and then, like...

01:29:31.553 --> 01:29:33.691
...sex could be, like,
nauseating for you?

01:29:33.827 --> 01:29:36.523
What are you, nuts?
Your wife's right over there.

01:29:38.832 --> 01:29:40.561
I'm just kidding, Muumuu!

01:29:40.834 --> 01:29:43.701
I now pronounce you man and wife.

01:29:48.842 --> 01:29:51.310
Mazel tov!

01:29:52.346 --> 01:29:54.439
It's very cold, so when you're ready...

01:29:54.848 --> 01:29:58.477
...put on a jacket and come have
breakfast with me. Love you.

01:30:30.384 --> 01:30:35.481
Hey, hey! Good morning, Mrs. Roth.
Would you like to meet your daughter?

01:30:35.889 --> 01:30:37.151
Go say hello to Mommy.

01:30:38.892 --> 01:30:40.553
Hi, Mommy.

01:30:42.896 --> 01:30:44.887
That's right.

01:30:46.400 --> 01:30:48.027
Good morning.

01:30:49.903 --> 01:30:52.064
Oh, my goodness!

01:30:52.906 --> 01:30:55.238
